1725:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   * @retval HAL status
1726:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   */
