3035:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   * @brief  Configure the analog watchdog.
3036:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   * @note   Possibility to update parameters on the fly:
3037:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         This function initializes the selected analog watchdog, successive
3038:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         calls to this function can be used to reconfigure some parameters
3039:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         of structure "ADC_AnalogWDGConfTypeDef" on the fly, without resetting
3040:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         the ADC.
3041:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         The setting of these parameters is conditioned to ADC state.
3042:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         For parameters constraints, see comments of structure
3043:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         "ADC_AnalogWDGConfTypeDef".
3044:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, analog watchdog thresholds can be modified
3045:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         while ADC conversion is on going.
3046:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         In this case, some constraints must be taken into account:
3047:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         the programmed threshold values are effective from the next
3048:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         ADC EOC (end of unitary conversion).
3049:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         Considering that registers write delay may happen due to
3050:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         bus activity, this might cause an uncertainty on the
3051:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         effective timing of the new programmed threshold values.
